Revision history for Perl extension Parallel::Dragons.

0.9.4  2016-06-26
  - startdocker - the Dragon doesn't detach, but forks childs

0.9.3  2016-06-26
  - documentation

0.9.2  2016-05-01 19:00:00
  - expose if the daemon is running in the foreground
  - BUGfix: _task_done was not called when running in fg
  - pre_start also runs with startfg

0.9.1  2016-04-26 17:15:00
  - support for a idle method
  - expose the number of childs running

0.9.0  2016-04-05 21:00:00
	- original version; Just imported and rename from what
      was currently in use.


